{"tid":351327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新渡輪籲船長航行避開油塊","createTime":"2017-08-08T02:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T04:32:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a867fa0b4fa9b68bb61fb160ba01b7d5df61ad86","tid":351327,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:47:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20114935&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20114935%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170808&d=t%2BWyz07Ewekxg3Ao4U6eyWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=042d7677\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20114935%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170808&h=3b536f72\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20114935&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170808</a><br />\n<br />\n新渡輪籲船長航行避開油塊<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170808/large/08la2p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170808%2Flarge%2F08la2p5.jpg&h=482ab0b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新渡輪昨提醒船長航行時避免駛過油脂層。周子惇攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】棕櫚硬脂襲港情況加劇，疑似油污更入侵維港，令人擔心影響船隻航行安全，海事處關注事件，提醒船隻航行時加倍小心。新渡輪已提醒船長避免駛過海面較厚的油脂層或油塊，以免影響船隻過濾系統，妨礙船隻航行安全，但暫時未接獲相關報告。天星小輪則指油污未影響其航線或船隻運作。<br />\n中環海面昨出現較多疑似油污，經營中環至長洲及梅窩航線的新渡輪已提示船長航行時避免駛過海面較厚油脂層，因船隻底部有吸口，航行時吸入海水冷卻機器，過程中海水會經過濾，但若船隻駛過較厚油脂層，可能吸入較多油脂並影響過濾系統，但發言人強調暫時未接獲船隻吸入油脂受影響的報告。<br />\n海事處指，因應處方安排船隻在香港西面及南面海域清理，已向駛經涉事水域船隻發出航行安全通告，提醒船隻航行時加倍小心。<br />\n■記者關英傑<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n疑吃污染物　南丫島死魚激增<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n油污湧入赤柱　海事處增派9船清理 泳客照落水　「成身油淋淋」<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;5小時前"},{"pid":"4ee4137a7c323a769873576c06f01ff50369ab93","tid":351327,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170808/large/08la2p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170808%2Flarge%2F08la2p1.jpg&h=cc60be49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【赤柱聖士提反灣】<br />\n泳灘昨受油污侵襲，有泳客照樣嬉水。<br />\n易仰民攝"},{"pid":"d488c3230ede00638c88ef59d920e2e75c777f1e","tid":351327,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:50:02.000Z","msg":"多謝中國厚禮"},{"pid":"ab2633cc84687491a13486076c03f2ea1d5d69b6","tid":351327,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170808/large/08la2p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170808%2Flarge%2F08la2p2.jpg&h=42efb9aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【南丫島蘆鬚城泳灘】<br />\n昨天氣酷熱，部份湧上泳灘的棕櫚硬脂開始融化。"},{"pid":"ccf2a3a4fb536d38eac5df86a3fc76f5c04a5bd4","tid":351327,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"國際災難"},{"pid":"31252f85a0cc2f524c78acfc4e3c067191376181","tid":351327,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T03:29:02.000Z","msg":"死仆街整撚曬啲油黎香港"},{"pid":"9d181d84fb723afdfc0d690fee1b32c345b8da10","tid":351327,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:32:55.000Z","msg":"支那送大禮，支那媒體提都唔提"}]}